headline: CDL: Little To Show, Look At SCHD Instead
summary: VictoryShares US Large Cap High Div Volatility Wtd ETF has a portfolio of dividend stocks selected based on yield and weighted based on volatility. Read why the SCHD ETF is a better choice.

headline: PPL Trades Above 50 & 200-Day SMAs: Time to Buy or Hold the Stock?
summary: PPL is benefiting from rising demand in its service territories, yet our suggestion for investors is to wait and look for a better entry point as the stock is trading at a premium.
